*Napustio* je dom i otišao u grad. (He left the house and went to the city.)

*Napuštala* je svoje prijatelje. (She was leaving her friends.)

*Napuštanje* je bilo teško. (The leaving was hard.)

*Napustiti* će mesto. (He will leave the place.)

*Napušten* je bio u teškoj situaciji. (He was abandoned in a difficult situation.)

*Napuštanja* nema. (There is no leaving.)